data.description: WELCOME HOME to 916 William Street with its picturesque landscape and beautiful surrounding views! Just minutes from Lehigh University, SteelStacks, and historic downtown Bethlehem. This comfortable, tastefully updated 4 bedroom/2.5 bath Cape Cod has everything you have been looking for. A sun-filled and inviting living room with rigid core luxury vinyl flooring and a wood burning fireplace. A completely remodeled kitchen and dining room with hardwood floors, beautiful granite countertops, tile backsplash, white cabinets and recessed lighting. A master suite oasis with spacious sitting room, plenty of storage space, a newly remodeled master bath and stunning new deck. New roof and windows installed in 2018 and new water heater and central air conditioning system installed in 2019. Don’t delay, schedule your showing TODAY!
